# Custom Output
---------------

_Value output customization._

_Function returns custom values, takes two parameters, code parameter receives the abbreviations! below you will see all types in the acronym table._

## abbreviations
    Reset
    - Reset Color_Off='0m'#Text 
   
    Regular Colors
    -------------- 
    - Black="0;30m"# Black
    - Red="0;31m"# Red
    - Green="0;32m"# Green
    - Yellow="0;33m"# Yellow
    - Blue="0;34m"# Blue
    - Purple="0;35m"# Purple
    - Cyan="0;36m"# Cyan
    - White="0;37m"# White

    Bold
    ----
    - BBlack="1;30m"# Black
    - BRed="1;31m"# Red
    - BGreen="1;32m"# Green
    - BYellow="1;33m"# Yellow
    - BBlue="1;34m"# Blue
